  "summary": "Moderate: libsndfile:1.0.31 security update",
  "details": "libsndfile is a C library for reading and writing files containing sampled sound, such as AIFF, AU, or WAV.   \n\nSecurity Fix(es):  \n\n  * libsndfile: Segmentation fault error in ogg_vorbis.c:417 vorbis_analysis_wrote() (CVE-2024-50612)\n\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.\n",
